reviews.review_text:
Acoustic Set has arrived Been waiting for this acoustic set to finally surface in a SBD and here it is. Its beautiful, as expected.
Thank you Charlie.

Charlie's Passion Project! Will Charlie be satisfied with perpetual recognition for his contribution to the high quality of the Archive's GD collection? I hope so... Thanks for the passion! 
I've built a business for 30 years and I know it takes a certain level of professionalism and a mental focus to get at it consistently enough to make it exist!
Support The Archive, preserve Charlie's (and all those folks) legacy! And of course, The Dead! When you get familiar, its totally worth the investment...
